Key Match Events: Max O'Dowd scored an unbeaten 54* to guide Netherlands to a six-wicket win over Nepal
Logan van Beek took 3 wickets for 18 runs to help Netherlands restrict Nepal to 106 all out
Post-Match Reflections: Scott Edwards, Netherlands captain, expressed satisfaction with the team's performance and praised Max O'Dowd's innings
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played in Dallas, Texas, USA
This was Nepal's first World Cup appearance since 2014
Others: The Netherlands moved to the top of Group D with the win, while Nepal are yet to register a victory
